comments: Valanciunas (NOP) brings his hand toward Holiday's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs during Holiday's drive.
Holiday (MIL) slips the contact with Alvarado (NOP) and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Holiday (MIL) rests his hand on McCollum's (NOP) side and marginal contact occurs during McCollum's drive.
McCollum (NOP) briefly grasps and then quickly releases Lopez's (MIL) jersey as he engages on the pick.
Connaughton (MIL) is retreating his arm into a vertical position and absorbs the marginal contact that occurs with Alvarado (NOP) after his gather.

During the pursuit of the rebound, Holiday (MIL) briefly grasps Williamson's (NOP) arm and marginal contact occurs before he cleanly deflects the ball away. Any lower body follow-through contact with Lopez (MIL) is deemed incidental.
Valanciunas (NOP) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Lopez's (MIL) layup attempt.
Matthews (MIL) has his arm in a vertical position and absorbs the marginal contact that occurs with Williamson (NOP) after his gather.
Allen (MIL) and Valanciunas (NOP) both make clean contact with the ball as Allen secures the rebound.
Williamson (NOP) brings his arm toward Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs during Antetokounmpo's drive.
Valanciunas (NOP) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Valanciunas (NOP) initiates contact with Lopez's (MIL) body, which affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Allen (MIL) is retreating alongside McCollum's (NOP) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Alvarado (NOP) briefly rests his hand on Holiday's (MIL) body as he moves alongside of him and marginal contact occurs as he attempts to deflect away the inbounds pass.
Alvarado (NOP) commits a take foul on Holiday (MIL).
Williamson (NOP) is established in Carter's (MIL) path and has his arm slightly extended when marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Matthews (MIL) moves alongside McCollum's (NOP) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Allen (MIL) maintains his pivot foot and then legally starts his dribble and passes the ball prior to his pivot foot returning to the ground.
Jones (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position alongside Allen (MIL) who loses his balance trying to come to a stop and prior to any incidental contact.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Lopez (MIL) throws an errant pass out of bounds and the Pelicans are correctly awarded possession.
Allen (MIL) legally contests and cleanly blocks Alvarado's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Valanciunas (NOP) moves into and makes contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body, which affects Antetokounmpo's SQBR.
Holiday (MIL) legally contests McCollum's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
